#: ../wiki/en/Server-Linux.md:20
msgid ""
"Enable the headless server process via systemd: `sudo systemctl enable "
"jamulus-headless`"
msgstr ""
"Activez le processus de serveur sans tête via systemd : `sudo systemctl "
"enable jamulus-headless`."

